title: Muffin Top Bakery
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Take-out, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Has a nice selection of vegan pastries and fresh breads which change daily, including cinnamon raisin bread, muffins, cream horns, brownies, apple turnovers, baklava, cupcakes and more. Customers can also special order vegan pies and cakes with a 24-hour notice. Also serves a variety of hot and cold coffee drinks which you can order with soy milk. There are about eight tables inside. Thursdays are market nights.
